My personal dotfiles :

DESCRIPTION :

- bash_profile : personal configuration for bash
- dir_colors : basic dircolors file for OSX
- dircolors-solarized : custom dircolors for the solarized theme
- gitconfig : personal configuration of git
- tmux.conf : configuration for tmux
- mailrc : mailx's configuration

HOW TO INSTALL :
    cd && git clone https://github.com/nyorem/dotfiles
    ln -s dotfiles/bash_profile .bash_profile
    ln -s dotfiles/gitconfig .gitconfig
    ln -s dotfiles/gitk .gitk
    ln -s dotfiles/tmux.conf .tmux.conf
    ln -s dotfiles/mailrc .mailrc
